    "enDesc": "Written by Gershon Henoch Leiner of Radzin (1839–1891), Ptil Tekhelet discusses the laws of the tekhelet, the blue dye used for the fringe of the tzitzit (tallit katan). The Rebbe made use of his knowledge in several scientific fields to discover the source of the tekhelet dye and promoted the use of tekhelet in tzitzit. ",
